{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/gatsbyBlog_9/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"gatsby-트러블슈팅\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gatsby-%ED%8A%B8%EB%9F%AC%EB%B8%94%EC%8A%88%ED%8C%85\" aria-label=\"gatsby 트러블슈팅 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Gatsby 트러블슈팅</h2>\n<p>[Gatby Blog 만들기]의 마지막 주제로, Gatsby를 사용하면서 발생하는 몇몇 이슈와 해결 방법에 대해여 논의해 본다. </p>\n<h3 id=\"excerpt-출력이-잘-안되는-문제\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#excerpt-%EC%B6%9C%EB%A0%A5%EC%9D%B4-%EC%9E%98-%EC%95%88%EB%90%98%EB%8A%94-%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C\" aria-label=\"excerpt 출력이 잘 안되는 문제 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Excerpt 출력이 잘 안되는 문제</h3>\n<p>Gatsby를 사용하면서 가장 처음 직면한 문제는 다음과 같이, 영어(latine Language)가 아니면 Excerpt를 잘 출력하지 못하는 이슈이다. Excerpt가 제대로 동작하지 않는 경우, 다음과 같이 포스팅글을 출력하는데에도 문제가 있을 뿐만 아니라, 검색엔진이 제대로 검색을 못해주는 경우가 발생할 수 있다. 실제로, 검색엔진의 최적화 가이드에서 Description이 부족하다는 경고를 하기도 한다. </p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Excerpt는 Gatsby가 사용하는 본문 요약으로써, meta tag의 description에 표기한다. </p>\n</blockquote>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>NO Excerpt (포스팅글의 요약이 빠져있다.)</th>\n<th>목표로 하는 결과물</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/795987c0e3d530e1640e45577de49691/a6d36/image-20210611172416271.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 81.75675675675677%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image-20210611172416271\"\n        title=\"image-20210611172416271\"\n        src=\"/static/795987c0e3d530e1640e45577de49691/fcda8/image-20210611172416271.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/795987c0e3d530e1640e45577de49691/12f09/image-20210611172416271.png 148w,\n/static/795987c0e3d530e1640e45577de49691/e4a3f/image-20210611172416271.png 295w,\n/static/795987c0e3d530e1640e45577de49691/fcda8/image-20210611172416271.png 590w,\n/static/795987c0e3d530e1640e45577de49691/a6d36/image-20210611172416271.png 650w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></td>\n<td><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ef54942415d33a01904eae2005ad7a62/a1253/gFPsoZqTjDk6bU4csUYfjfB5QEGxpjJETTo1bsmOKv5Lc5itFumiOu3trT23D8pcGelK3kC0lnG70474plQlaZK5XD3l0eGUmssdMEF4LdaCMTYxZpq_xaJ6v2f5_-dh-SmCeEhZaVg.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 91.8918918918919%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"/static/ef54942415d33a01904eae2005ad7a62/fcda8/gFPsoZqTjDk6bU4csUYfjfB5QEGxpjJETTo1bsmOKv5Lc5itFumiOu3trT23D8pcGelK3kC0lnG70474plQlaZK5XD3l0eGUmssdMEF4LdaCMTYxZpq_xaJ6v2f5_-dh-SmCeEhZaVg.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ef54942415d33a01904eae2005ad7a62/12f09/gFPsoZqTjDk6bU4csUYfjfB5QEGxpjJETTo1bsmOKv5Lc5itFumiOu3trT23D8pcGelK3kC0lnG70474plQlaZK5XD3l0eGUmssdMEF4LdaCMTYxZpq_xaJ6v2f5_-dh-SmCeEhZaVg.png 148w,\n/static/ef54942415d33a01904eae2005ad7a62/e4a3f/gFPsoZqTjDk6bU4csUYfjfB5QEGxpjJETTo1bsmOKv5Lc5itFumiOu3trT23D8pcGelK3kC0lnG70474plQlaZK5XD3l0eGUmssdMEF4LdaCMTYxZpq_xaJ6v2f5_-dh-SmCeEhZaVg.png 295w,\n/static/ef54942415d33a01904eae2005ad7a62/fcda8/gFPsoZqTjDk6bU4csUYfjfB5QEGxpjJETTo1bsmOKv5Lc5itFumiOu3trT23D8pcGelK3kC0lnG70474plQlaZK5XD3l0eGUmssdMEF4LdaCMTYxZpq_xaJ6v2f5_-dh-SmCeEhZaVg.png 590w,\n/static/ef54942415d33a01904eae2005ad7a62/a1253/gFPsoZqTjDk6bU4csUYfjfB5QEGxpjJETTo1bsmOKv5Lc5itFumiOu3trT23D8pcGelK3kC0lnG70474plQlaZK5XD3l0eGUmssdMEF4LdaCMTYxZpq_xaJ6v2f5_-dh-SmCeEhZaVg.png 657w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>위 그림은 실제 필자의 블로그에서 포스팅글에 요약내용이 <code class=\"language-text\">...</code> 으로만 표기되어 있는 경우이다. 이 문제는  매우 오랫동안 진행되어온 이슈로 영어 등의 Latin Language 계열이 아닌 다른 언어의 경우에 발생하는 문제이다. </p>\n<p>검색엔진의 웹마스터 도구 및 최적적화 도구에서도 다음과 같은 경고 문구를 출력하고 있다. Meta tag의 Description이 너무 짧다는 경고 이다. 아래 6건은 Description이 <code class=\"language-text\">...</code> 으로만 등록되어 있는 경우이다. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/69c19270fe969400145f29aadf5444c0/0fb99/bIWANjxept-Z6WzWORE2gsm8HOes0IvxoD2H3MvRrnkYHGnAr_O7C_gnxZooK_Hr-TSN9sY4pm1BxwqsE-YVTC_leWpNE8FeEBO5NCyipFSUTNuGRjHHUY7uugP-fvlbeTCNmOkjS4k.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 4.72972972972973%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAABCAIAAABR8BlyAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAM0lEQVQI1z2ISQ4AIAjE/P8/BTEs43aXE8m0aaZNEaY+BoukyE0NcMQ9uxbGG/qyFpL6P50BN/tR9T30AAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"/static/69c19270fe969400145f29aadf5444c0/fcda8/bIWANjxept-Z6WzWORE2gsm8HOes0IvxoD2H3MvRrnkYHGnAr_O7C_gnxZooK_Hr-TSN9sY4pm1BxwqsE-YVTC_leWpNE8FeEBO5NCyipFSUTNuGRjHHUY7uugP-fvlbeTCNmOkjS4k.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/69c19270fe969400145f29aadf5444c0/12f09/bIWANjxept-Z6WzWORE2gsm8HOes0IvxoD2H3MvRrnkYHGnAr_O7C_gnxZooK_Hr-TSN9sY4pm1BxwqsE-YVTC_leWpNE8FeEBO5NCyipFSUTNuGRjHHUY7uugP-fvlbeTCNmOkjS4k.png 148w,\n/static/69c19270fe969400145f29aadf5444c0/e4a3f/bIWANjxept-Z6WzWORE2gsm8HOes0IvxoD2H3MvRrnkYHGnAr_O7C_gnxZooK_Hr-TSN9sY4pm1BxwqsE-YVTC_leWpNE8FeEBO5NCyipFSUTNuGRjHHUY7uugP-fvlbeTCNmOkjS4k.png 295w,\n/static/69c19270fe969400145f29aadf5444c0/fcda8/bIWANjxept-Z6WzWORE2gsm8HOes0IvxoD2H3MvRrnkYHGnAr_O7C_gnxZooK_Hr-TSN9sY4pm1BxwqsE-YVTC_leWpNE8FeEBO5NCyipFSUTNuGRjHHUY7uugP-fvlbeTCNmOkjS4k.png 590w,\n/static/69c19270fe969400145f29aadf5444c0/efc66/bIWANjxept-Z6WzWORE2gsm8HOes0IvxoD2H3MvRrnkYHGnAr_O7C_gnxZooK_Hr-TSN9sY4pm1BxwqsE-YVTC_leWpNE8FeEBO5NCyipFSUTNuGRjHHUY7uugP-fvlbeTCNmOkjS4k.png 885w,\n/static/69c19270fe969400145f29aadf5444c0/0fb99/bIWANjxept-Z6WzWORE2gsm8HOes0IvxoD2H3MvRrnkYHGnAr_O7C_gnxZooK_Hr-TSN9sY4pm1BxwqsE-YVTC_leWpNE8FeEBO5NCyipFSUTNuGRjHHUY7uugP-fvlbeTCNmOkjS4k.png 965w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>다음은 Graphql을 직접 질의했을 때의 결과이다. 마찬가지로, excerpt 항목의 결과가 \"...\"으로 반환 되는 것을 확인 할 수 있다. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c3bab695d325483de7fc1e0fe4b831b3/df5d6/image-20210611173205529.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 38.513513513513516%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image-20210611173205529\"\n        title=\"image-20210611173205529\"\n        src=\"/static/c3bab695d325483de7fc1e0fe4b831b3/fcda8/image-20210611173205529.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c3bab695d325483de7fc1e0fe4b831b3/12f09/image-20210611173205529.png 148w,\n/static/c3bab695d325483de7fc1e0fe4b831b3/e4a3f/image-20210611173205529.png 295w,\n/static/c3bab695d325483de7fc1e0fe4b831b3/fcda8/image-20210611173205529.png 590w,\n/static/c3bab695d325483de7fc1e0fe4b831b3/efc66/image-20210611173205529.png 885w,\n/static/c3bab695d325483de7fc1e0fe4b831b3/c83ae/image-20210611173205529.png 1180w,\n/static/c3bab695d325483de7fc1e0fe4b831b3/df5d6/image-20210611173205529.png 2514w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"해결-방안\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0-%EB%B0%A9%EC%95%88\" aria-label=\"해결 방안 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>해결 방안</h3>\n<p>사실, 이 이슈는 매우 오랫동안 알려져 있는 문제이다. Gatsby의 \"markdownRemark\"의 non-Latin Language support 문제이다. Gatsby Plugin에서도 공식 Trubleshooting으로 제공하는 제용으로써, graphql에서 질의할 때, excerpt항목에 아래와 같은 옵션을 추가함으로써 해결할 수 있다. </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">excerpt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>truncate<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>실제 공식 가이드에는 다음과 같이 소개되고 있다. </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">Excerpts for non-latin languages\nBy default, excerpt uses underscore.string/prune which doesn’t handle non-latin characters (https://github.com/epeli/underscore.string/issues/418).\nIf that is the case, you can set truncate option on excerpt field, like:\n{\n  markdownRemark {\n    excerpt(truncate: true)\n  }\n}</code></pre></div>\n<p>필자의 블로그에서 GraphQL 에디터에 질의문을 변경하여 정상 출력 되는 것을 확인 할 수 있다. </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\">query <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    allMarkdownRemark(filter<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>frontmatter<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>title<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>ne<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> sort<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> fields<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>frontmatter___date<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> order<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> DESC <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> limit<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span>) <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      edges <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        node <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          excerpt(format<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> PLAIN<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> truncate<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>)\n          fields <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            slug\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n          frontmatter <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            date(formatString<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"MMM DD, YYYY\"</span>)\n            update(formatString<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"MMM DD, YYYY\"</span>)\n            title\n            category\n            tags\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>수정사항 : 6번 라인에서 <code class=\"language-text\">excerpt(format: PLAIN, truncate: true)</code> </p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>결과적으로 다음과 같이 Excerpt가 정상 출력되고, 이 에 따라 포스팅글의 요약문과 Description을 정상입력할 수 있다. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6fe0d3dd5c251dce9b1de920eeac2151/a1253/VCkuyjuAJ6gMFxbPjsjQaOc1Euglikzm1P75miFtKH12wT5P-g1UOfD_1gJsZcvv6TX61KmE9KW1UsbYVKHVxoydh1vjKgmRWeduBPEbuf3e7pgLO5ykbAU4fMNQRRNl7Y5G_jQmKUg.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 91.8918918918919%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"/static/6fe0d3dd5c251dce9b1de920eeac2151/fcda8/VCkuyjuAJ6gMFxbPjsjQaOc1Euglikzm1P75miFtKH12wT5P-g1UOfD_1gJsZcvv6TX61KmE9KW1UsbYVKHVxoydh1vjKgmRWeduBPEbuf3e7pgLO5ykbAU4fMNQRRNl7Y5G_jQmKUg.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6fe0d3dd5c251dce9b1de920eeac2151/12f09/VCkuyjuAJ6gMFxbPjsjQaOc1Euglikzm1P75miFtKH12wT5P-g1UOfD_1gJsZcvv6TX61KmE9KW1UsbYVKHVxoydh1vjKgmRWeduBPEbuf3e7pgLO5ykbAU4fMNQRRNl7Y5G_jQmKUg.png 148w,\n/static/6fe0d3dd5c251dce9b1de920eeac2151/e4a3f/VCkuyjuAJ6gMFxbPjsjQaOc1Euglikzm1P75miFtKH12wT5P-g1UOfD_1gJsZcvv6TX61KmE9KW1UsbYVKHVxoydh1vjKgmRWeduBPEbuf3e7pgLO5ykbAU4fMNQRRNl7Y5G_jQmKUg.png 295w,\n/static/6fe0d3dd5c251